  <para>
    When the mouse becomes the moving cross-hair, you can use the keyboard
    arrow keys to move the crop rectangle. Holding the
    <keycap moreinfo="none">Shift</keycap> key down allows to move by steps of 25 pixels.
  </para>
  <para>
    You can use Guides to position the crop area. Make sure that the
    <menuchoice moreinfo="none">
      <guimenu moreinfo="none">View</guimenu>
      <guimenuitem moreinfo="none">Snap to Guides</guimenuitem>
    </menuchoice>
    option is checked.
  </para>

  
  

  
  

  
  

